statements: SELECT * FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing
SELECT InspectorName, MeasurementValue, MeasurementDate FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing ORDER BY MeasurementDate DESC
SELECT SampleID, InspectorName FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementValue > 100
SELECT * FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementDate BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31'
SELECT SampleID, MeasurementValue, MeasurementUnit FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing ORDER BY SampleID ASC
SELECT * FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementValue > 50 ORDER BY MeasurementDate DESC, InspectorName ASC
SELECT SampleID, InspectorName, MAX(MeasurementValue) AS MaxValue FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing GROUP BY SampleID, InspectorName
SELECT AVG(MeasurementValue) AS AverageValue, MeasurementUnit FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementUnit = 'mm' GROUP BY MeasurementUnit
SELECT SampleID, MeasurementValue FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementDate BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY SampleID, MeasurementDate DESC
SELECT SampleID, MeasurementValue, MeasurementDate FROM QualityControlMeasuresInNanotechManufacturing WHERE MeasurementValue < 30 AND MeasurementUnit = 'nm' ORDER BY MeasurementValue ASC
SELECT * FROM quality_control LIMIT 10;
SELECT product_name, manufacturing_date FROM quality_control WHERE quality_standard = 'ISO 9001';
SELECT inspector_name, manufacturing_date, quality_standard FROM quality_control ORDER BY manufacturing_date DESC;
SELECT product_name, measurement_date, measurement_value FROM quality_control qc LEFT JOIN measurement_data md ON qc.id = md.product_id WHERE qc.product_name LIKE 'Product%';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM quality_control;
SELECT product_name, manufacturing_date FROM quality_control WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM quality_control WHERE manufacturing_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT inspector_name, quality_standard, product_name FROM quality_control WHERE quality_standard LIKE '%ISO%';
SELECT * FROM quality_control ORDER BY manufacturing_date DESC;
SELECT product_name, measurement_value FROM quality_control JOIN measurement_data ON quality_control.id = measurement_data.product_id WHERE measurement_value > 50;
SELECT qc_id, parameter_name, measurement_result FROM quality_control;
SELECT standard_name, description FROM compliance_standards;
SELECT process_id, process_name, location FROM manufacturing_processes;
SELECT qc_id, parameter_name FROM quality_control WHERE measurement_result > 5.0;
SELECT standard_name FROM compliance_standards WHERE standard_name LIKE 'ISO%';
SELECT qc_id, measurement_result, process_id FROM quality_control WHERE qc_id = 1;
SELECT standard_name, description FROM compliance_standards WHERE standard_id = 5;
SELECT process_name, start_date, end_date, location FROM manufacturing_processes WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT qc_id, parameter_name, measurement_result FROM quality_control WHERE measurement_result < 10 ORDER BY measurement_result ASC;
SELECT qc_id, process_name, measurement_result FROM quality_control qc JOIN manufacturing_processes mp ON qc.process_id = mp.process_id WHERE measurement_result > 5 ORDER BY process_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM QualityControlMeasures ORDER BY manufacturing_date DESC;
SELECT manufacturer, standard_compliance FROM QualityControlMeasures WHERE standard_compliance = TRUE;
SELECT standard_name, regulatory_body FROM NanotechnologyStandards WHERE description LIKE '%nanotechnology%';
SELECT * FROM ProductQualityAssessment WHERE passed_quality_test = FALSE;
SELECT message, log_date FROM ComplianceLogs ORDER BY log_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM QualityControlMeasures WHERE standard_compliance = TRUE;
SELECT standard_name, description FROM NanotechnologyStandards WHERE regulatory_body = 'FDA';
SELECT manufacturer, manufacturing_date FROM QualityControlMeasures ORDER BY manufacturing_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM ProductQualityAssessment WHERE passed_quality_test = FALSE;
SELECT id, log_date, message FROM ComplianceLogs;
SELECT * FROM quality_control_measures;
SELECT qc_name, qc_description FROM quality_control_measures WHERE qc_id = 1;
SELECT manufacturer_name, manufacturer_location FROM nanotechnology_manufacturing ORDER BY manufacturer_name DESC;
SELECT standard_id, standard_name, standard_description FROM standards WHERE standard_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT record_id, record_date, compliance_status FROM compliance_records WHERE compliance_status = TRUE ORDER BY record_date DESC;
SELECT qc_name, qc_description FROM quality_control_measures;
SELECT standard_name, standard_description FROM standards ORDER BY standard_name DESC;
SELECT manufacturer_name, manufacturer_location FROM nanotechnology_manufacturing WHERE manufacturer_location LIKE '%USA%';
SELECT qc_name, qc_description, qc_date FROM quality_control_measures WHERE qc_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT record_id, qc_name, standard_name, manufacturer_name, record_date FROM compliance_records JOIN quality_control_measures ON compliance_records.qc_id = quality_control_measures.qc_id JOIN standards ON compliance_records.standard_id = standards.standard_id JOIN nanotechnology_manufacturing ON compliance_records.manufacturer_id = nanotechnology_manufacturing.manufacturer_id ORDER BY record_date DESC;
